# Copy to .env.local and fill in real values. Never commit .env.local (already gitignored).
#
# No provider API key goes here -- users bring their own Claude/GPT/Gemini key through
# the form at request time. It is never persisted server-side.

# Optional: raises the GitHub API rate limit from 60/hr to 5000/hr. Needs no scopes for
# auditing public repos - a plain classic token with no permissions checked is enough.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
